            <title><![CDATA[🎉 flutter_inapp_purchase 6.0.0-rc.1 Release Candidate - StoreKit 2 & Billing Client v8 Support]]></title>
            <link>https://flutter-iap.hyo.dev/blog/flutter-iap-6.0.0-rc-release</link>
