<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="-whats-next">🔜 What's Next<a href="https://flutter-iap.hyo.dev/blog/flutter-iap-6.0.0-rc-release#-whats-next" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 🔜 What's Next" title="Direct link to 🔜 What's Next">​</a></h2>
