<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="-how-to-try-the-release-candidate">📥 How to Try the Release Candidate<a href="https://flutter-iap.hyo.dev/blog/flutter-iap-6.0.0-rc-release#-how-to-try-the-release-candidate" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to 📥 How to Try the Release Candidate" title="Direct link to 📥 How to Try the Release Candidate">​</a></h2>
